What are some examples of how you've demonstrated creativity in your work?
Last year, I redesigned our company's website to better reflect our brand identity and mission statement. I used a minimalist color scheme, clean typography, and clear navigation menus that made the site visually appealing yet easy to use. I also incorporated interactive elements like infographics and multimedia galleries into the design, which helped engage visitors with our content while providing valuable insights about what we do best.
